node.text:
SO excited that I finally get to announce that debut EP collab is launching July 27th 🙌 

We want 8 of YOU to join us for the exclusive Zoom launch party hosted by Emily 🎉 Thurs 7/15 at 7pm est AND you’ll receive pieces from the collection this week!!! 

How to enter:

1: Follow @electricpicks & me
2: Comment your fav emoji below

*Extra entry by tagging a jewelry loving friend!

*You’ll also receive a surprise gift box...pssst it’s pretty exclusive 🤗 

Winners will be announced tomorrow!!

node.text: Biggest congrats to Mr. & Mrs. Blood 🤍 We danced the night away & I’m just happy my dress stayed up 😅 Lee was tightening my strap in the Uber and it broke 🙈 So he just tied it tight & luckily we had no nip slips 😂
